20/* Id */
21
22#ifndef ISC_INT_H
23#define ISC_INT_H 1
24
25/*! \file */
26
27typedef char isc_int8_t;
28typedef unsigned char isc_uint8_t;
29typedef short isc_int16_t;
30typedef unsigned short isc_uint16_t;
31typedef int isc_int32_t;
32typedef unsigned int isc_uint32_t;
33typedef long long isc_int64_t;
34typedef unsigned long long isc_uint64_t;
35
36#define ISC_INT8_MIN -128
37#define ISC_INT8_MAX 127
38#define ISC_UINT8_MAX 255
39
40#define ISC_INT16_MIN -32768
41#define ISC_INT16_MAX 32767
42#define ISC_UINT16_MAX 65535
43
44/*%
45 * Note that "int" is 32 bits on all currently supported Unix-like operating
46 * systems, but "long" can be either 32 bits or 64 bits, thus the 32 bit
47 * constants are not qualified with "L".
48 */
49#define ISC_INT32_MIN -2147483648
50#define ISC_INT32_MAX 2147483647
51#define ISC_UINT32_MAX 4294967295U
52
53#define ISC_INT64_MIN -9223372036854775808LL
54#define ISC_INT64_MAX 9223372036854775807LL
55#define ISC_UINT64_MAX 18446744073709551615ULL
56
57#endif /* ISC_INT_H */
58
